---
const signs = [
  "Frequent repairs",
  "High energy bills",
  "Inconsistent heating",
  "Systems over 15 years old"
];
---

<section class="mb-16">
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Heating System Replacement and Upgrades</h2>
  <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
      If your current system is outdated or inefficient, it may be time for a heating system upgrade. We offer seamless heating system replacements, providing modern systems that deliver better performance and lower operating costs.
    </p>
    
    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Signs you need a replacement:</h3>
    <ul class="space-y-3">
      {signs.map(sign => (
        <li class="flex items-center text-gray-600">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          {sign}
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>